web-player.settings.personalized-recomme: Okwenzayo ku-Spotify okwamanje kwenzelwe wena ngokusekelwe kuphrofayela yakho yokuthandwayo. Ukuvala lokhu kuzokwenza kube okuvamile.
Okunconwayo kokuthi Isiqalo nakuyo yonke indawo ku-Spotify (komculo, ama-podcast, nama-audiobook)
Izinhla zokudlalayo ezenzelwe wena, ezifana nezithi Zitholele Kwangeviki, Imiksi Yangemihla, kanye ne-daylist
Okuqukethwe okusha kwabaculi nemibukiso oyilandela ngokucacile
Le sethingi ithinta wonke amadivayisi. Kungase kube khona ukulibala ngaphambi kokuthi ubhekane nezinguquko.
Okwenzayo ku-Spotify kuvamile esikhundleni sokuthi kwenzelwe wena ngokusekelwe kuphrofayela yakho yokuthandwayo.
Ungavula okunconywayo komuntu siqu nganoma yisiphi isikhathi Kumasethingi.

web-player.user-comments.trust-safety-mo: Ingabe usukulungele ukushiya ukuphawula kwakho kokuqala ku-Spotify?
Sibheke phambili ukuzwa kuwena. Kodwa okokuqala, nazi izinto ezimbalwa okufanele uzikhumbule.
Ukuphawula kwakho, igama, nesithombe sephrofayela sizobonakala kwabanye ku-Spotify uma iphrofayela yakho ibonakala emphakathini.
Ukuphawula kwakho kungase kudinge ukugunyazwa okwengeziwe ngaphambi kokuthi kubonakale kwabanye.
Ungakwazi ukususa ukuphawula kwakho, ubike okulimazayo, futhi uvimbe amanye ama-akhawunti.
Ukuze uthole ulwazi olwengeziwe, funda %platformRules% yethu kanye%termsOfUse%
Kufanele uvumelane nalokhu okungenhla ukuze uqhubeke.

web-player.pigeon.introduction.step-1.su: Sakaza ngaphandle kwezintambo kuze kufike ku-16-bit noma ku-24-bit kumadivayisi ahambisanayo usebenzisa Ukuxhuma ku-Spotify.
web-player.pigeon.introduction.step-2.su: Bheka ilebula ethi Njengoba Unjalo ukuze ubonise lapho usakaza kuze kufike ku-16-bit noma ku-24-bit.
web-player.pigeon.introduction.step-3.su: Awukutholi okuthi Njengoba Unjalo? Hlola amathiphu ethu ochwepheshe okusakaza futhi uxazulule inkinga ngokuthepha.
web-player.pigeon.introduction.step-4.su: Ungakwazi ukulungisa ikhwalithi yomsindo wokusakaza Nokudawunilodiwe kokuthi Amasethingi.
search.empty-results-text-short: Zama ukusesha futhi usebenzisa isipelingi esihlukile noma igama eliyinhloko.

Kopisha futhi yabelana ngesixhumanisi nabangane bakho, noma ubacele ukuthi baskene ikhodi ye-QR.
web-player.social-connect.broadcasting.t: Vumela abanye basebenzise i-Jam kulesi sipikha
npv.related-videos.title: Amavidiyo omculo ahlobene
web-player.now-playing-view.dubbed-episo: Lalela lesi siqephu ngolimi oluncamelayo, ngokuhumusha kwezwi okukhiqizwe ngomshini.
Izwa lesi siqephu ngokuhumusha kwezwi okukhiqizwe ngomshini.
web-player.now-playing-view.original-epi: Lesi siqephu ekuqaleni sasikhulunywa ngolunye ulimi.
web-player.social-connect.promotion.how-: Ungaqalisa i-Jam nganoma yisiphi isikhathi ngokusebenzisa imenyu yokuchofoza kwesokudla.
web-player.puffin.activation-dialog.subt: Ngeke uthole umsindo owandisiwe wamahedifoni akho.
web-player.pigeon.get-started.title: Lahleka kumsindo othi Njengoba Unjalo
web-player.pigeon.get-started.subtitle: Sakaza kuze kufike ku-24-bit kunoma iyiphi idivayisi ehambisanayo.
web-player.puffin.activation-2.title: Ingabe usebenzisa {0}?
web-player.puffin.activation-1.title: Ingabe ukulungele ukuthola okwengeziwe kumahedifoni akho?
web-player.puffin.activation-3.title: Impumelelo! Amahedifoni akho aselungile.
web-player.puffin.activation-3.subtitle: Bheka okucwebezelayo ukuze wazi lapho ukuthuthukisa sekusebenza.
web-player.puffin.device-connection-lost: Qiniseka ukuthi amahedifoni akho axhunyiwe. Zama ukuwaqalisa kabusha.
Qiniseka ukuthi kuxhunywe isethi eyodwa yamahedifoni.
Usebenzisa izipikha noma enye idivayisi? Ukuthuthukisa kutholakala kuphela kumahedifoni athile.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.listen-offl: Lalela kokuthi Njengoba unjalo, ungaxhunyiwe ku-inthanethi
Dawuniloda umculo wakho kokuthi Njengoba Unjalo ukuze ulalele kukhwalithi yethu ephezulu kakhulu ngenkathi ungaxhunyiwe ku-inthanethi. Buyekeza ikhwalithi yokudawuniloda kokuthi Amasethingi.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.connect-exp: Indlela engcono kakhulu yokulalela kokuthi Njengoba Unjalo iwukusebenzisa Ukuxhuma ku-Spotify. Vele udlale ingoma, bese uthepha okuthi {0} ngezansi kwesikrini ukuze ukhethe idivayisi futhi ulawule umculo wakho ukusuka ngqo ohlelweni.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.bluetooth-d: Ukusebenzisa i-Bluetooth kuzothinta ukulalela kokuthi Njengoba unjalo

Amadivayisi amaningi e-Bluetooth akwazi ukudlala ikhwalithi yomculo engcono kunokuthi Okuphezulu Kakhulu, kodwa awawusekeli ngokugcwele umsindo wokuthi Njengoba unjalo. Okuthi Njengoba Unjalo kujatshulelwa kangcono ngezipikha zokuXhuma ku-Spotify kanye/noma amadivayisi anezintambo.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.opt-out-of-: Shintsha amasethingi akho ukuze ujabulele ukulalela okushelela kakhudlwana

Usukhubazé isici sekhwalithi esizilungisa sona Kumasethingi. Lokhu kusho ukuthi ungase uphazamiseke ekulaleleni kwakho uma une-bandwidth ebuthaka ye-inthanethi. Ungavula lesi sici kokuthi Amasethingi.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.poor-bandwi: Kubonakala sengathi i-bandwidth yakho ye-inthanethi inenkinga yokusekela okuthi Njengoba unjalo njengamanje. Zama ukuhlola ukuxhuma kwakho noma ushintshele kunethiwekhi ehlukile.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.default-to-: Shintsha amasethingi akho ukuze usakaze ngokuthi Njengoba unjalo

Ayikho into ephoxa njengokweqa kwengoma. Yingakho sikwehlisa ngokuzenzakalelayo kusuka kokuthi Njengoba Unjalo ukuya kukhwalithi yomsindo ephansi uma une-bandwidth ebuthaka. Ungavala isici sekhwalithi esizilungisa sona kokuthi Amasethingi.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.need-to-red: Dawuniloda kabusha izingoma zakho ukuze uzidlale kokuthi Njengoba unjalo

Izingoma ozidawunilodile okwamanje azikho kokuthi Njengoba unjalo. Uma ufuna ukuzilalela kokuthi Njengoba unjalo, uzodinga ukuzidawuniloda kabusha. Ungakhohlwa phela ukuthi amafayela ezingoma zokuthi Njengoba unjalo makhulu futhi angasebenzisa isitoreji esiningi kakhulu. Ungashintsha ikhwalithi yomsindo wamadawunilodi akho kokuthi Amasethingi.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.lossless-un: Siyaxolisa, le threkhi ayitholakali kokuthi Njengoba unjalo okwamanje.
web-player.pigeon.help-cards.update-sett: Shintsha amasethingi akho ekhwalithi yomsindo ukuze usakaze kokuthi Njengoba unjalo
Usethe Amasethingi akho ukuthi adlale umculo kokuphezulu noma okuphansi Kakhulu. Ukuze ushintshe lokhu, iya kokuthi Amasethingi bese ukhetha okuthi Njengoba Unjalo.
web-player.social-connect.broadcasting.s: Abantu abaningi bangakwazi ukujoyina nokulawula lesi sipikha
web-player.social-connect.broadcasting.j: Abantu abaku-Jam bazobona igama lakho lomsebenzisi, isithombe sephrofayela, nezingoma eziphakanyisiwe ngokusekelwe kuphrofayela yakho yokuthandwayo.
web-player.connect.nudge.dj-voice-unavai: Ku-beta, izwi lika-DJ alitholakali kulesi sipikha
web-player.puffin.reset-headphones.dialo: Lokhu kuzophinde kusethe kabusha izinga lakho lokwenza umsindo ube ovamile. Lawula izinga lokwenza kube okuvamile ngekhasi Kumasethingi.
web-player.puffin.manual-selection.empty: Zama ukusesha futhi usebenzisa isipelingi esihlukile noma igama eliyinhloko.
web-player.puffin.dismiss-get-started.bo: Ngeke siphinde sinikeze lokhu kuthuthukiswa kule divayisi. Lokhu akukwazi ukuhlehliswa.
web-player.puffin.error-troubleshooting: Uxolo, lokhu akutholakali. Zama ukuxhuma kabusha amahedifoni akho.
